channel.title: You Have Not Unlocked This Yet
channel.description: When I try most commands, as a mod it tells me, "you have not unlocked this yet". When i try the command Unlockmenow, it still tells me the same thing. I know there are different commands for Mods/Pmods/Admins, but I still get the error on mod only commands.
